where \(\bm{P}_{f}\in\mathbb{R}^{\frac{n}{7}\times n}\) is a matrix that implements a block averaging filter to downscale the images by a factor of \(f\). Specifically, we set \(f=4\) and used the SVD implementation from the code3 of [39].

